ewest first): [msg100, msg99, msg98, msg97, msg96, msg95] for limit=5\nSlice to 
5: [msg100, msg99, msg98, msg97, msg96]\nReverse: [msg96, msg97, msg98, msg99, m
sg100]\nnextCursor = messages[0].sequence_id = 96\n\nNext query with cursor=96: 
