s the expected chat UI behavior.\n\nHowever, `_scrollToBottom` scrolls to `maxSc
rollExtent`, which is the end of the list (newest messages). Good.\n\nOne more i
ssue: In `ImBloc._onMessageReceived`, when a message is received for the current
